snippet.title: Genshin Impact | Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Genshin Impact is an open world action game set in the fantasy world called “Teyvat”, offering players a freely explorable world, multiple playable characters, an in-depth elemental combo-based combat system and an engaging story. Developed and published by miHoYo, the title is scheduled to come to PlayStation plaftform in 2020.
